  "title": "F&B Full Time Service Crew @ FUNAN/NTU/HOUGANG/MILLENIA WALK",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Full Time Service Crew at YATSUDOKI AND CHATERAISE!!!</strong></u></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<p>· To deliver excellent customer service</p>\n<p>· Hande cashiering system, various payment mode and devices</p>\n<p>· Taking and packing orders for customers</p>\n<p>· Ensure shelves are continuously stocked</p>\n<p>· Maintaining cleanliness of store</p>\n<p>· Cross sell and up sell products</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>· Minimum GCE “N” level</p>\n<p>· Have some experience in F&amp;B industry</p>\n<p>· Cheerful persona and able to work as a Team</p>\n<p>· Able to work in a fast pace environment</p>\n<p>· Full timers: 6 days work week (48hrs/week, including weekends and public holiday, rotating shifts), 9am - 6pm/12-10.30pm, from $2,200 (basic)</p>\n<p>· Available immediately preferred</p>\n<p>· Benefits for full timers: 10 days annual leave, training and uniforms will be provided.</p>\n<p>· Work Location: <strong>Millenia Walk, Funan, Tampines West, NTU and Hougang Rivercourt</strong></p>\n<p>· Part time positions available at $12.09/hour</p>\n<p>. Interested candidates please email CV (<strong>please include your contact number</strong>) to sg_recruitment@chateraise-i.com <strong>(No Agents please/ No Quota)</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>",
